additionalProperty.name: Ingredients
additionalProperty.value: Glycerin, PEG-8, Hydrated Silica, Calcium Sodium Phosphosilicate (NOVAMIN), Aroma, Soidum Lauryl Sulfate, Sodium Monofluorophosphate, Titanium Dioxide, Carbomer, Sodium Saccharin, Eugenol, Limonene. Contains Sodium Monofluorophosphate 1.08%w/w (1450ppm Fluoride).

additionalProperty.name: Warning
additionalProperty.value: Sensitive teeth may indicate an underlying problem that needs prompt care. If symptoms persist or worsen consult your dentist. Talk to your Dentist or Doctor as soon as possible if you experience swelling of the mouth or face. If irritation occurs discontinue use. Do not swallow. Not for use by children 12 years of age or under unless on the advice of a dental professional or doctor. Keep out of reach of children. Do not use if foil seal on nozzle is broken. Sensitive teeth may indicate an underlying problem that needs prompt care by a dentist. If irritation occurs, discontinue use.
